snippet.title: Snake Infinity Game Trailer 4S
snippet.description:
Slither and glide through this stark and starry 3D galaxy to your top score! A fresh and exciting twist on a classic arcade game, Snake Infinity takes you to new heights. This simulated snake game gives players first person perspective to make advancing your score that much more thrilling. Touch controls provide players the ability to easily discover the coveted apples. Beware of the galactic cage walls, and don’t be shut down by your own deadly, ever-growing tail. Four different levels provide an intense challenge for even the most stealthy of snakes!

https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id963932767?mt=8&ign-mpt=uo%3D6
